{"title_page": "United States men's national basketball team", "text_new": "{{Redirect|United States national basketball team|the women's team|United States women's national basketball team}}\n{{Redirect|Team USA Basketball|the video game|Team USA Basketball (video game)}}\n{{short description|National sports team}}\n{{Infobox national basketball team\n| current            = 2019 United States FIBA Basketball World Cup team\n| country            = United States {{flagicon|USA}}\n| logo               = File:Usa basketball 2012.png\n| logo_width         = 160px\n| nickname           = ''Team USA''\n| coach              = [[Jeff Van Gundy]]:<br>''[[2017 FIBA AmeriCup|FIBA AmeriCup]]''<br>''[[2019 FIBA Basketball World Cup qualification (Americas)|FIBA World Cup Qualifiers]]''<br>[[Gregg Popovich]]:<br>''[[2019 FIBA Basketball World Cup|FIBA World Cup]]''<br>''[[Basketball at the 2020 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|Olympic Games]]''\n| FIBA_ranking       = {{FIBA World Rankings|USA|mdy=y}}\n| joined_FIBA        = 1934\n| FIBA_zone          = FIBA Americas\n| national_fed       = [[USA Basketball]]\n| oly_appearances    = 18\n| oly_medals         = {{OG1}} ''Gold:'' ([[1936 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1936]], [[1948 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1948]], [[1952 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1952]], [[1956 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1956]], [[1960 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1960]], [[1964 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1964]], [[1968 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1968]], [[1976 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1976]], [[1984 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1984]], [[1992 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1992]], [[1996 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1996]], [[2000 United States men's Olympic basketball team|2000]], [[2008 United States men's Olympic basketball team|2008]], [[2012 United States men's Olympic basketball team|2012]], [[2016 United States men's Olympic basketball team|2016]])<br>{{OG2}} ''Silver:'' ([[1972 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1972]])<br>{{OG3}} ''Bronze:'' ([[1988 United States men's Olympic basketball team|1988]], [[2004 United States men's Olympic basketball team|2004]])\n| wc_appearances     = 17\n| wc_medals          = {{World1}} ''Gold:'' ([[1954 FIBA World Championship|1954]], [[1986 FIBA World Championship|1986]], [[1994 FIBA World Championship|1994]], [[2010 United States men's FIBA World Championship team|2010]], [[2014 United States FIBA Basketball World Cup team|2014]])<br>{{World2}} ''Silver:'' ([[1950 FIBA World Championship|1950]], [[1959 FIBA World Championship|1959]], [[1982 FIBA World Championship|1982]])<br>{{World3}} ''Bronze:'' ([[1974 FIBA World Championship|1974]], [[1990 FIBA World Championship|1990]], [[1998 FIBA World Championship|1998]], [[2006 FIBA World Championship|2006]])\n| zone_championship  = [[FIBA AmeriCup]]\n| zone_appearances   = 9{{ref label|N|N|Na}}\n| zone_medals        = {{Panamgold}} ''Gold:'' ([[1992 Tournament of the Americas|1992]], [[1993 Tournament of the Americas|1993]], [[1997 Tournament of the Americas|1997]], [[1999 Tournament of the Americas|1999]], [[2003 Tournament of the Americas|2003]], [[2007 FIBA Americas Championship|2007]], [[2017 FIBA AmeriCup|2017]])<br>{{Panamsilver}} ''Silver:'' ([[1989 Tournament of the Americas|1989]])\n| zone2_championship = \n| zone2_appearances  = \n| zone2_medals       = \n| h_title = Home\n| h_body = FFFFFF\n| h_pattern_b = _usabk16h\n| h_shorts = FFFFFF\n| h_pattern_s = _usabk16h\n| a_title = Away\n| a_body = 002B54\n| a_pattern_b = _usabk16a\n| a_shorts = 002B54\n| a_pattern_s = _usabk16a\n| 3_title =\n| 3_body =\n| 3_pattern_b =\n| 3_shorts =\n| 3_pattern_s =\n| first_game         = {{bk|USA|1912}} 2\u20130 {{bk-rt|ESP|1931}} {{Small|(forfeit)}}<br>[[Berlin]], [[Nazi Germany|Germany]] \u2013 August 7, 1936\n| largest_win        = {{bk|USA}} 156\u20137