007 FIBA Americas Championship squads#United States|2007 FIBA Americas Championship]]\n*'''[[2017 FIBA AmeriCup squads#United States|2017 FIBA AmeriCup]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n==See also==\n*[[United States men's national under-19 basketball team]]\n*[[United States men's national under-17 basketball team]]\n*[[United States men\u2019s national 3x3 team]]\n*[[United States women's national basketball team]]\n*[[United States women's national under-19 basketball team]]\n*[[United States women's national under-17 basketball team]]\n*[[United States women's national 3x3 team]]\n*[[USA Basketball]]\n*[[Basketball in the United States]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{refbegin}}\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n* {{note label|N|N|Na}}{{note label|N|N|Nb}} In 2001, the U.S. was represented by [[National Junior College Athletic Association|NJCAA]] players. USA Basketball doesn't include their results in the [https://www.usab.com/history/national-team-mens/fiba-americup-all-time-scores.aspx national team]'s record.\n{{col-end}}\n{{refend}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons}}\n\n*[https://www.usab.com/mens/national-team.aspx Official website]\n*[http://archive.fiba.com/pages/eng/fa/p/tid/379/_/teams.html FIBA Profile]\n*[https://www.basketball-reference.com/awards/uso.html U.S. Olympic Basketball Team Rosters and Stats]\n\n{{United States men's national basketball team}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n|title = United States men's national basketball team squads\n|bg = #FFFFFF\n|fg = #212844\n|bordercolor = #C22032\n|list1 =\n{{Navboxes colour\n| title=United States Olympic Games squads\n| bg= #FFFFFF\n| fg= #212844\n| bordercolor= #C22032\n| list1=\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1936 Summer Olympics}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1948 Summer Olympics}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1952 Summer Olympics}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1956 Summer Olympics}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1960 Summer Olympics}}\n{{United States Men B