A Americas Championship}}\n{{United States squad 2007 FIBA Americas Championship}}\n{{United States squad 2017 FIBA AmeriCup}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n| title=United States Pan American Games squads\n| bg= #FFFFFF\n| fg= #212844\n| bordercolor= #C22032\n| list1=\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1951 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1955 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1959 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1963 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1967 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1975 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1979 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1983 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1987 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1991 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1995 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 1999 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 2011 Pan American Games}}\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 2015 Pan American Games}}\n}}\n}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Links to related articles\n| titlestyle    = background:#FFFFFF; color:#212844; {{box-shadow border|a|#C22032}}\n|list =\n{{FIBA Basketball World Cup winners}}\n{{Summer Olympics basketball men's tournament winners}}\n{{USA Basketball Male Athlete of the Year}}\n{{FIBA Basketball World Cup hosts}}\n{{FIBA Americas teams}}\n{{Basketball in the United States}}\n{{National sports teams of the United States}}\n}}\n\n[[Category:United States men's national basketball team| ]]\n[[Category:National basketball teams]]\n[[Category:National sports teams of the United States|Basketball]]\n[[Category:1934 establishments in the United States]]\n[[Category:Sports clubs established in 1934]]\n", "name_user": "Adventghuyt", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States_men%27s_