le          = \n| ridertype     = \n| amateuryears1 = \n| amateurteam1  = \n| proyears1     = \n| proteam1      = \n| majorwins     = \n}}\n\n'''M\u00e1rio Silva''' (born 5 October 1940) is a Portuguese former [[cycling|cyclist]]. He competed in the [[Cycling at the 1960 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's individual road race|individual road race]] and [[Cycling at the 1960 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's team time trial|team time trial]] events at the [[1960 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"sports-reference\">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/si/mario-silva-1.html |title=M\u00e1rio Silva Olympic Results |accessdate=29 July 2014 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Silva, Mario}}\n[[Category:1940 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Portuguese male cyclists]]\n[[Category:Olympic cyclists of Portugal]]\n[[Category:Cyclists at the 1960 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Volta a Portugal winners]]\n{{Portugal-cycling-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Lugnuts", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/M%C3%A1rio_Silva_(cyclist)"}
